Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:06.94,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}I know you. You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:11.86,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}無論何時你溫柔的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.00,0:24:15.10,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}我都想要獨自占有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:18.73,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}不禁如此期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:21.48,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}吶 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:26.49,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}想讓這成為我戀愛的起點
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.62,0:24:28.24,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}最喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.24,0:24:31.53,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur5}在你的身邊
